"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-simone-biles-olympics-paris-2024-gymnastics-b2586466.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The most decorated gymnast in history heads to Paris seeking to add yet more medals to her collection  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999471433526, \"rank\": 5.285650173726586e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Simone Bilesshould have little left to prove.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Themost decorated gymnast in history, the American already has a haul of 37 World and Olympic medals in her collection, 27 of them glittering gold.\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999197800989311, \"rank\": 7.91530746869337e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For nearly a decade, the 27-year-old has been the standout figure in her sport, her name and reputation evidence of excellence, Biles cutting through culturally as one of the world'smost popular and prominent athletes.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Biles will head to her thirdOlympicsatParis 2024with a few bad memories to banish.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After a remarkable debut in Rio brought four gold medals to establish herself asgymnastics' ruling queen, her career nearly came crashing down entirely in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999800277217182, \"rank\": 1.9972677282413056e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.765125965938587, \"rank\": 0.3069743037322676, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The problems began on her opening day of competition.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Performing the all-around during qualification, Biles made a number of uncharacteristic errors, almost coming a cropper onboth the vault and the balance beam.Such is her ability that the Texan still managed to make all of the individual finals but something was clearly wrong.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On social media, Biles suggested that she was feeling \\\"the weight of the world on [her] shoulders\\\" - and worse was yet to come.The infamous 'twisties'(a temporary loss of air awareness) left Biles unable to complete her rotations, forcing her to withdraw from several events.\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having overcome her mental block, Biles returned forbattle on the balance beam,nabbing a second medal to go along with team silver.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was another two years before she would be seen in competition again.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I say put mental health first,\\\" Biles said of her decision to step away in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2022, \"end\": 2027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.765125965938587, \"rank\": 0.3069743037322676, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because if you do not, then you are not going to enjoy your sport and you are not going to succeed as much as you want to.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's OK sometimes to even sit out the big competitions to focus on yourself, because it shows how strong of a competitor and person that you really are - rather than just battle through it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not just in the arena that Biles has had battles to overcome.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2018, the gymnast revealed that she hadbeen sexually abused by Larry Nassar,the disgraced former team doctor of the US Gymnastics team.\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2482, \"end\": 2494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"score\": 0.9999997290624746, \"rank\": 2.709377822209101e-07, \"text\": \"Larry Nassar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\"}, {\"begin\": 2538, \"end\": 2548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9919292700810133, \"rank\": 0.008129947497872296, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nassar is serving between 40 and 175 years in prison for sexually abusing young female athletes in his care, with Biles among those testifying at the Senate in 2021 about how the system had failed to protect her.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2555, \"end\": 2561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8685438261344812e-36, \"text\": \"Nassar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\"}, {\"begin\": 2705, \"end\": 2711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Senate\", \"score\": 0.5466530027357716, \"rank\": 0.6209569274531246, \"text\": \"Senate\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Senate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Senate\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After attending regular therapy, Biles at last felt ready to make her comeback last August.\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anticipation abounded as she stepped back into elite gymnastics atthe US Classic in Chicago.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2931, \"end\": 2933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8996592006577326, \"rank\": 0.11129163370893998, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2945, \"end\": 2952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.9999970421738996, \"rank\": 2.13466134698654e-06, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What level would Biles be at after so long away?\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The answer was emphatic: a dominant all-around victory.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A month and a half later, a return to top level was underlined by four golds and a silver at the World Championships in Belgium:her antics in Antwerpwere proof that Biles was most certainly back.\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3179, \"end\": 3186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9831662744366706, \"rank\": 0.016918802379447956, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was emotional, and it means everything,\\\" Biles said afterwards.\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The fight, everything that I have put in to get back to this place, feel comfortable and confident enough to compete.\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a lot.\\\"\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A return to the Olympics now offers an opportunity to cement her legacy.\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her tilt at six gold medals three years ago may have ended in disappointment but Biles could once more target an historic haul in Paris.\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3662, \"end\": 3667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999471433526, \"rank\": 5.285650173726586e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American sits five golds behind Larisa Latynina, the most successful female gymnast at the Games, on the all-time list.\", \"from\": 3670, \"to\": 3793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3674, \"end\": 3682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999197800989311, \"rank\": 7.91530746869337e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3706, \"end\": 3721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larisa Latynina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A repeat of Rio would vault her into rarified air, and anything more into history - after the turmoil and torment of Tokyo, Biles appears ready to shine again.\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3806, \"end\": 3809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999800277217182, \"rank\": 1.9972677282413056e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3911, \"end\": 3916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.765125965938587, \"rank\": 0.3069743037322676, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 4185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4006, \"end\": 4017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2998826327945705e-18, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"